Shreve Chiropractic Cycling Challeng
description: Road race event from 27 to 45 miles on a 9 mile loop.
course: Challenging 9 mile loop through the village of shreve and surrounding Amish countryside. Starts in town flat with gradual rollers out of town and then steep 1 mile hill followed by rollers and down hill to very sharp curve. Rolling hills the remainder of the route back to town with a few technical turns. New finish line up a gradual hill. Cat V, juniors and women will go 3 laps, Cat IV 4 laps and Cat II-III 5 laps.
registration: Registration by mail or at event.  Registration closes 9am day of race.
directions: Take US route 30 to Wooster,Ohio, to route 3 south, to 226 South to shreve.  Registration is at Shreve Elementary schoool just inside city limits on left hand side, can\\\'t miss the sign.
